              "rest": "3 minutes between sets",
              "tempo": "controlled eccentric, explosive concentric",
              "notes": "Wave loading exploits post-activation potentiation. Heavy sets (85%, 87%) prime the nervous system, making subsequent moderate sets (77%, 82%) feel lighter and allowing higher quality reps at near-maximal intensities. This is a Week 2-3 intensity scheme for experienced lifters.",
              "rpe": null,
