      "rationale": {
        "session_why": {
          "text": "Push press develops explosive upper body power through leg drive integration. E2MOM format maintains consistent output across 8 sets, building work capacity at 75% intensity. The For Time metcon creates glycolytic demand through descending rep ladder, emphasizing upper body pushing and pulling with midline stability holds. Total session emphasizes vertical pressing power and upper body stamina.",
