          "url_or_ref": "Chapter on body tension fundamentals"
        },
        "loading_why": {
          "text": "E2MOM straight sets at 75% of 1RM builds hypertrophy and strength-endurance. The 2-minute interval provides adequate phosphocreatine recovery for power movements while maintaining session flow and athlete engagement. This format auto-regulates rest: faster execution earns more recovery time. 8 rounds \u00d7 4 reps = 32 total reps at moderate-high intensity, appropriate for Week 1-2 baseline volume accumulation without excessive CNS fatigue.",
          "source": "Bompa & Haff - Periodization 5th ed",
          "url_or_ref": "Chapter 6 - Hypertrophy training parameters"
        }
