          "text": "Gymnastics skill session emphasizing vertical pressing in the handstand position, a fundamental bodyweight strength skill. Hollow and arch holds are mandatory foundational tension work. The For Time metcon creates upper body stamina through high-volume pulling, pushing, and posterior chain work. This session develops coordination, balance, and body control (3 of the 10 physical skills) while building upper body work capacity.",
