        "loading_why": {
          "text": "Gymnastics skill work is prescribed at RPE 7-8 with full rest (90-120 sec) between sets to preserve movement quality. Volume is kept moderate (5 sets \u00d7 3-5 reps) to prevent technical degradation under fatigue. This is not conditioning - it is skill acquisition. Quality of movement execution matters more than total rep count. Athletes scale to appropriate progression level (pike push-ups if needed) to maintain perfect form throughout all sets.",
